Title: The Moon Jumping
Author: সাবরিনা করিম
Summary: The story revolves around Sammy, who does not believe that cows can jump over the moon and Moo, a cool Bermuda shorts wearing, shade toting bull who wants to do a hat trick in Moon Jumping at the Cowrnival. But all is not that easy in this side of the story-verse as Sammy and Moo will make friends and meet foes. This is a tale that will take the young readers for a joyride into a unique imaginary world and teach the importance of friendship and difference between right and wrong.
